{"tid":1378712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞中催淚彈小朋友下文","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:03:32.000Z","uid":199332,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1486f4f01fd02dbef412ee2a921687ad6ca9cd82","tid":1378712,"uid":199332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"頭先發夢喺皇后大道中嘅時候<br />\n見到有位爸爸帶住佢兩位小朋友向西環方向行<br />\n但我哋一路退緊去反方向<br />\n見到小朋友個樣已經好辛苦<br />\n我唯有大叫佢哋唔好行去嗰邊 危險呀<br />\n但佢爸爸似乎冇反應<br />\n有手足追上前 叫佢哋快啲走<br />\n原來係大陸人嚟嘅 個爸爸仲話要返屋企 要繼續行<br />\n有手足就幫嗰兩個小朋友洗眼<br />\n最後佢哋先返轉頭走 <br />\n但兩個小朋友係咁喊<br />\n<br />\n但我想講呢段嘢嘅重點 唔係兩個小朋友有幾慘 黑警放催淚彈有幾狼死 而係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你哋班人頭豬 宜家香港搞緊革命呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解你哋仲可以施施然行出街 食花生睇表演咁<br />\n班狗已經癲咗㗎喇 <br />\n喺你屋企樓下都會放催淚彈開槍㗎<br />\n唔該你哋注意下自己安全 翻安全嘅地方啦好嘛<br />\n唔想再有咁多無辜嘅人受傷呀"},{"pid":"de3929fc7abd8c8efa45fc2d55b98b9364fb7bb6","tid":1378712,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82469891fbe64c2d30384c67c98a6d2aa4665e91","tid":1378712,"uid":199332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"求下你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a9c34ace2d13731f055af9d70a1153a661562c","tid":1378712,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4714af20dd8b60596e3b9bb54a4663e855b5487","tid":1378712,"uid":199332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"香港真係好唔安全㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以唔好亂咁帶小朋友出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a0811755c96f0095c8818e2073ef8f001094f","tid":1378712,"uid":199332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"不過黑警亂放催淚彈 <br />\n民居小朋友都食晒 <br />\n一定要煲大佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec6c56bab7e16d6ebe002f973644806096731d5","tid":1378712,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a9c34ace2d13731f055af9d70a1153a661562c","tid":1378712,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"其實點掉先可以掉到咁？"},{"pid":"3716e298c0d8f1625462c8f937eeff1b6344c6c0","tid":1378712,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ec6c56bab7e16d6ebe002f973644806096731d5","tid":1378712,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a9c34ace2d13731f055af9d70a1153a661562c","tid":1378712,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"其實點掉先可以掉到咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"瞄住囉"},{"pid":"1f6bd63da673c84b0f14bf1af4cc28ebcdb0b44d","tid":1378712,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ec6c56bab7e16d6ebe002f973644806096731d5","tid":1378712,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a9c34ace2d13731f055af9d70a1153a661562c","tid":1378712,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,